{"tid":1007280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平「一國兩制」講話後 台獨支持度急升12%","createTime":"2019-02-03T15:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T10:06:34.000Z","uid":144372,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3e75f223688c371937b37be6ba9e6835d087aa23","tid":1007280,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:57:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/習近平-一國兩制-講話後-蔡英文民望谷底急升-近半台灣人撐台獨/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6-%E8%AC%9B%E8%A9%B1%E5%BE%8C-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E8%B0%B7%E5%BA%95%E6%80%A5%E5%8D%87-%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%8A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BA%BA%E6%92%90%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A8%2F&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=d08c2e5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6-%E8%AC%9B%E8%A9%B1%E5%BE%8C-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E8%B0%B7%E5%BA%95%E6%80%A5%E5%8D%87-%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%8A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BA%BA%E6%92%90%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A8%2F&h=6e984031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/習近平-一國兩制-講話後-蔡英文民望谷底急升-近半台灣人撐台獨/</a><br />\n台灣民意調查基金會發表最新民意調查，顯示總統蔡英文的民望，在月初中國國家主席習近平發表《告台灣同胞書》40 周年講話後急升。「總統職務表現贊同率」在十數日內急升 10 個百分點至 34.5 %，為去年 6 月以來新高，但仍然低於48%的不贊同率。另外，有 47.5 %的受訪者支持台灣獨立，比上月主張台獨的人，大升 12個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文的民意支持度自去年 6 月以來，本來一直在低位徘徊，12月份民望跌至 24.3 %，在「習講話」後則反彈，「總統職務表現贊同率」大幅提升10個百分點，達34.5%，也是去年6月以來最高的時刻，連原本創歷史新高的「總統職務表現不贊同率」也從60%下降到48%。<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現，有四成三人滿意蔡英文處理兩岸關係表現，比上月增加了近 18 個百分點；有四成九人不滿意，較上月減少 17 個百分點。報告稱，民意態度起伏之大「前所未見」，認為蔡英文的聲望出現如此強勁的「谷底反彈」，脫離她上任以來兩岸關係處理不佳的困境，主要是受到「中國效應」刺激所致，習近平「意外的、無心的」幫蔡英文「鹹魚翻生」，是百分百「非其所願的後果」。"},{"pid":"8d2a79d38addd631ccea55189d1946b3cc0d1a79","tid":1007280,"uid":147292,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:01:47.000Z","msg":"功成不必在我"},{"pid":"30edd29ee9ed80c310c071b907ae8101b478ab8f","tid":1007280,"uid":21545,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"小學生真係小學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243006a7aae26973fb14e40ed55c57f61a5707a9","tid":1007280,"uid":41245,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"台灣人唔輸啲位畀國民黨都唔知死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早知今日會反返支，當初就唔好轉投藍啦"},{"pid":"48455e8d947780678d231838fe564ffa196fc8e5","tid":1007280,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T18:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99834c725ac0d64e0d35c1edd0ac146475ae152b","tid":1007280,"uid":105366,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T18:44:01.000Z","msg":"「票投國民黨，臺灣變香港」始終係史上最有效既政治宣傳標語"},{"pid":"e17d6d8d6724be8cd585511cdbdd01b3ff7e68a8","tid":1007280,"uid":68620,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T18:51:30.000Z","msg":"香港變成咁多謝習9上台，上台後不停打壓香港言語自由，又亂將香港變成佢地推廣垃圾大亞灣，又要迫香港公司用埋d垃圾支那公司產品先會獲得好代如<br />\n多謝習9條79無讀過書搞到香港亂曬龍<br />\n前兩代都無鎖得咁緊，係習9條79"},{"pid":"017bc4b4d6e0ed7741a48be1a22f7292dfaf3984","tid":1007280,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T20:35:14.000Z","msg":"都話左習大大係分裂緊中共啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b9db042f1a111dac4d186b62823a06e7102469","tid":1007280,"uid":104112,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"8d2a79d38addd631ccea55189d1946b3cc0d1a79","tid":1007280,"uid":147292,"like":